                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step 1: ",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Visit Gram Panchayat or the nearest Government Veterinary Dispensary to collect the application form."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step 2:",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " Carefully fill in all the required details, including personal information, category details, and bank details."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step 3: ",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Attach photocopies of all the necessary documents (self-attested, if required) and submit the application form."
                    }
                  ]
